<section class="faqs mt-5" id="faqs">
    <h2 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="accordion w-100 h-5" id="basicAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading1">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse1" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse1">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>How often can I donate blood?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading1"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>There is a minimum waiting period between blood donations. This can vary depending on your blood type and gender. Generally, men can donate whole blood every 86 days (approximately 3 months), while women can donate every 112 days (approximately 4 months).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading2">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse2" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse2">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>What are the eligibility requirements for blood donation?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>
                                To donate blood, you must meet certain eligibility criteria, including:
                                <ol>
                                    <li>
                                        Age (usually between 17-60 years old, with some variations)
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Minimum weight (typically around 110 lbs)
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Overall good health (free from illness or recent vaccinations)
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Hemoglobin level (sufficient iron stores for blood production)
                                    </li>
                                </ol>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading3">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse3" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse3">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>
                                What health conditions prevent me from donating blood?
                            </h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading3"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>Certain medical conditions or medications may temporarily or permanently disqualify you from donating blood. It's best to check with a BloodNet representative or visit our website for a complete list.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading4">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse4" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse4">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>Will donating blood affect my health?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading4"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>Blood donation is a safe process. The amount of blood drawn is carefully regulated, and your body quickly replenishes the lost fluids. You may experience minor side effects like temporary fatigue or soreness at the injection site, which are usually mild and pass quickly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading5">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse5" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse5">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>What should I eat and drink before donating blood?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading5"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>It's important to be well-hydrated before donating blood. Drink plenty of fluids (water, juice) in the hours leading up to your donation. Eat a healthy meal beforehand to maintain your blood sugar levels and avoid feeling faint.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading6">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse6" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse6">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>What can I expect during the blood donation process?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading6"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>
                                The donation process typically involves several steps:
                            </p>

                            <ul>
                                <li>Registration: Completing a questionnaire about your health history and lifestyle.</li>
                                <li>Screening: Checking your temperature, blood pressure, and hemoglobin level.</li>
                                <li>
                                    Donation: The actual blood draw, which takes around 10-15 minutes.
                                </li>
                                <li>Refreshments: Relaxing for a few minutes and enjoying refreshments to replenish fluids.</li>
                            </ul>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading7">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse7" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse7">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>Is blood donation painful?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading7"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>You might feel a slight prick when the needle is inserted, but the overall process is not considered painful.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading8">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse8" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse8">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>Can I donate blood if I have a tattoo or piercing?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse8" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading8"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>Temporary eligibility restrictions may apply depending on the timing and location of your tattoo or piercing. It's best to refer to our website for details.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading9">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse9" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse9">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>What happens to my blood after I donate?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse9" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading9"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>Your donated blood undergoes rigorous testing and processing to ensure its safety. It's then separated into different components (red blood cells, plasma, platelets) and distributed to hospitals and medical centers for patients in need.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading10">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapse10" aria-expanded="false"
                            aria-controls="basicAccordionCollapse10">
                        <div class="container">
                            <h5>Why is blood donation important?</h5>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="basicAccordionCollapse10" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading10"
                     data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <div class="container">
                            <p>Blood donation is critical for saving lives and supporting various medical procedures. There's no substitute for human blood, and volunteer donors are the sole source for patients battling illnesses, injuries, or undergoing surgeries.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
</div>
        </div>
</section>


